{
  "stem": "4670.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He took the briefcase, which was new, and made it look old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He separated the lining.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He actually opened the lining-- I don't know exactly how.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But he pasted money inside there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There was newspaper that was in there, also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I-- I have no idea how a briefcase is lined.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But it took quite a while to do this, to make it look old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They put acid to make the-- the metal look older.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And he glued it back in such a way that you could not tell it had ever been disturbed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And then he decided he had to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We didn't have-- we-- in order to leave Germany at that point, you didn't need a visa.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I don't know how or-- or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "It was not like coming in the United States.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And he decided he was leaving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was extremely stressful, and I have pictures to show you from the day that my dad left.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Anyway, my dad left to go and our signal was that he was going to Strasbourg and he was going to call us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And we were very, very frightened because just two days before we left-- he left, a man, a friend of our family-- I don't know who he was-- also left Germany, and he had hidden some money in a bird cage.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "It was like a double floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "He had been taken off the train and we knew we never heard from this man again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "So I don't know what happened to him and we were very frightened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "My dad, I remember, he took a tranquilizer with him before he went on the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And with a heavy heart, we said goodbye to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "The-- the plan was, he was going to Strasbourg.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
